<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/findId.js" defer></script>
    <title>아이디 찾기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/findId.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="header-title">
                아이디 찾기
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p>가입 시 기재한 이름과 생년월일을 입력해주세요</p>
    <form name="findPw-form">
        <div class="name">
            <label for="name">이름</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" /><br />
        </div>
        <div class="birth">
            <label for="birth">생년월일</label>
            <div class="birth_select">
                <select name="year" id="birth-year">
                </select>
                <select name="month" id="birth-month">
                </select>
                <select name="day" id="birth-day">
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>    
        <div class="btn">
            <div class="findPw_btn">
                <button type="button" onclick="findPw()">찾기</button>
            </div>
            <div class="cancel_btn">
                <button type="button" onclick="cancel()">취소</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="result"></div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>